NOTE ON THE SHARP MODEL:

This project wraps the SHARP model by Apple. The model itself is distributed
under the Apple Machine Learning Research Model License Agreement, which
restricts use to non-commercial scientific research and academic development.
This wrapper is for personal, research, and educational use only. It does not
redistribute the model weights — they are downloaded directly from Apple's CDN
on first use.

See: https://github.com/apple/ml-sharp/blob/main/LICENSE_MODEL
